2-48-14/45.mp3","time_start":128.91,"time_end":132.05},{"position":46,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/46.mp3","time_start":132.05,"time_end":132.89},{"position":47,"content":"The front door opens onto the old farmyard,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/47.mp3","time_start":133.42,"time_end":136.64},{"position":48,"content":"and parking isn't a problem -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/48.mp3","time_start":136.82,"time_end":139.23},{"position":49,"content":"there's plenty of room at the front for that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/49.mp3","time_start":139.31,"time_end":141.9},{"position":50,"content":"There are some trees and potted plants there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/50.mp3","time_start":142.21,"time_end":145.14},{"position":51,"content":"What about facilities in the cottage?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/51.mp3","time_start":145.55,"time_end":148.35},{"position":52,"content":"It has standard things like a cooker and fridge, I presume.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/52.mp3","time_start":148.35,"time_end":152.57},{"position":53,"content":"In the kitchen area there's a fridge-freezer","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/53.mp3","time_start":153.12,"time_end":156.4},{"position":54,"content":"and we've just put in an electric cooker.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/54.mp3","time_start":156.52,"time_end":159.56},{"position":55,"content":"Is there a washing machine?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/55.mp3","time_start":160.13,"time_end":161.71},{"position":56,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/56.mp3","time_start":161.82,"time_end":162.74},{"position":57,"content":"There's also a TV in the living room, which plays DVDs too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/57.mp3","time_start":162.89,"time_end":167.8},{"position":58,"content":"The bathroom is too small for a bath,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/58.mp3","time_start":168.33,"time_end":171.09},{"position":59,"content":"so there's a shower instead.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/59.mp3","time_start":171.09,"time_end":173.22},{"position":60,"content":"I think a lot of people prefer that nowadays, anyway.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/60.mp3","time_start":173.5,"time_end":176.68},{"position":61,"content":"It's more environmentally friendly, isn't it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/61.mp3","time_start":176.79,"time_end":179.4},{"position":62,"content":"Unless you spend half the day in it!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/62.mp3","time_start":179.5,"time_end":181.68},{"position":63,"content":"Exactly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/63.mp3","time_start":181.68,"time_end":182.58},{"position":64,"content":"What about heating?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/64.mp3","time_start":182.71,"time_end":184.17},{"position":65,"content":"It sometimes gets quite cool at that time of year.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/65.mp3","time_start":184.35,"time_end":187.52},{"position":66,"content":"There's central heating, and if you want to light a fire, there's a stove.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/66.mp3","time_start":187.8,"time_end":192.71},{"position":67,"content":"We can provide all the wood you need for it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/67.mp3","time_start":192.87,"time_end":196.04},{"position":68,"content":"It smells so much nicer than coal,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/68.mp3","time_start":196.38,"time_end":198.69},{"position":69,"content":"and it makes the room very cosy -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/69.mp3","time_start":198.9,"time_end":201.08},{"position":70,"content":"we've got one in our own house.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/70.mp3","time_start":201.24,"time_end":203.12},{"position":71,"content":"That sounds very pleasant.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/71.mp3","time_start":203.27,"time_end":205.33},{"position":72,"content":"Perhaps we should come in the winter, to make the most of it!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/72.mp3","time_start":205.43,"time_end":208.45},{"position":73,"content":"Yes, we find we don't want to go out when we've got the fire burning.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/73.mp3","time_start":208.45,"time_end":212.85},{"position":74,"content":"There are some attractive views from the cottage, which I haven't mentioned.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/74.mp3","time_start":213.2,"time_end":217.76},{"position":75,"content":"There's a famous stone bridge -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/75.mp3","time_start":217.99,"time_end":220.49},{"position":76,"content":"it's one of the oldest in the region,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/76.mp3","time_start":220.65,"time_end":223.16},{"position":77,"content":"and you can see it from the living room.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/77.mp3","time_start":223.16,"time_end":225.32},{"position":78,"content":"It isn't far away.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/78.mp3","time_start":225.55,"time_end":227.2},{"position":79,"content":"The bedroom window looks in the opposite direction,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/79.mp3","time_start":227.74,"time_end":230.7},{"position":80,"content":"and has a lovely view of the hills and the monument at the top.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/80.mp3","time_start":230.84,"time_end":235.11},{"position":81,"content":"Well, that all sounds perfect.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/81.mp3","time_start":235.23,"time_end":237.9},{"position":82,"content":"I'd like to book it, please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/82.mp3","time_start":237.9,"time_end":239.56},{"position":83,"content":"Would you want a deposit?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/83.mp3","time_start":239.56,"time_end":241.23},{"position":84,"content":"Yes, we ask for 30% to secure your booking,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/84.mp3","time_start":241.32,"time_end":245.74},{"position":85,"content":"so that'll be... £144.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/85.mp3","time_start":245.81,"time_end":250.24},{"position":86,"content":"And when would you like the rest of the money?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/86.mp3","time_start":250.4,"time_end":252.89},{"position":87,"content":"You're coming in May, so the last day of March, please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/87.mp3","time_start":253.16,"time_end":257.92},{"position":88,"content":"Fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/88.mp3","time_start":258.05,"time_end":258.79},{"position":89,"content":"Excellent.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/89.mp3","time_start":258.97,"time_end":260.11},{"position":90,"content":"Could I just take your details...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-4-part-1-2023-01-05-22-48-14/90.mp3","time_start":260.34,"time_end":263.0}]}